# Warte, Iraq

Warte () is a town located in Rawanduz  district in Erbil Governorate, Kurdistan Region in Iraq. It is located between Choman and Soran. It lies 36 km (22 miles) from the city of Rawanduz and lies 30 km (18.6 miles) from the city of Ranya. It is populated by Kurds.
